== Syntax ==
<pre style="font-size:95%; overflow:auto;">
{{Collapsible list
|framestyle = <!--(optional)-->
|title = 
|titlestyle = <!--(optional)-->
|liststyle  = <!--(optional)-->
|1 =          <!--(First item in list)--->
|2 =          <!--(Second item in list)-->
|3 =          <!--(Third item in list)--->
|...
}}
</pre>

;Default state
Specifying <code>expand = true</code>, or any non-blank value, will set the default state to expanded.

